Quest:Adding the Frosting

From Wizard101 Wiki
Jump to: navigation, search

Quest Information


Prequest:
Playing with Fire
Note: Level 18 is needed to start this quest.
Note: In order to complete this quest, Wizards must be in the School of Balance.

Given By: Arthur Wethersfield

Giver Location: Ravenwood
This is a side quest.

Goals:
Talk to Zan'ne in the Krokotopia Library
Talk to Niles at the Krokosphinx
Get Icy Water in the Entrance Hall
Talk to Arthur Wethersfield in Ravenwood
Hand In: Arthur Wethersfield

Reward:

0
155


Leads to:

Take It by Storm (at level 18)

Quest Dialogue


This page is for recording a complete Quest Dialogue of all the conversation and story during a quest.
This includes NPC discussions, Narrator statements, and Creature speeches.


Documentation on how to edit this page can be found at Template:QuestInfobox/doc.

Hints, guides, and discussions of the Wiki content related to Adding the Frosting should be placed in the Wiki Page Discussion Forums.
